text: Quality construction and care is evident throughout this park model with add-a-room at the Glen at Maple Falls! Energy/efficiency updates include two heat pumps for heating and cooling, an additional electrical panel and an upgraded furnace. Bedroom on the main floor with additional sleeping space in the loft. Full bath and full size appliances in the kitchen. Covered deck for year-round enjoyment and a storage shed. Comes fully furnished and ready to go! Community amenities include Nooksack River access, parks, trails, pools, playgrounds, disc golf & year-round events. Gated access w/ 24/7 security. Located just 30 minutes form Bellingham & 15 minutes from the base of Mt. Baker & Silver Lake. Limited to 120 days/year occupancy. No rentals.

Rare opportunity to purchase nearly 4.3 acres of land in the highly sought-after Meridian School District. This property offers all utilities on site & includes a 1, 782 square foot manufactured home featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Situated at the end of E Axton, just beyond the bend on Starry Road, the property boasts a serene & secluded setting surrounded by natural beauty and mature trees. Enjoy the peaceful, country atmosphere while being just a short 15-minute drive from Lynden and Bellingham & minutes away from the scenic Shuksan Golf Course. The area offers a perfect blend of tranquility & convenience, with access to local farms, parks & outdoor recreation, making this property truly unique with endless possibilities.

This is the full lakefront package! The Fairhaven design is the largest tiny home, no joke. Features a spacious living and kitchen area, a front deck for sunshine, and a covered deck with Infratech heaters great for entertaining. Explore this unique layout with a two-bedroom loft, upper fireplace, and incredible rooftop deck for excellent star gazing. This includes a deep water boat slip in the Wildwood Marina, and access to all of the community resort amenities. If you are a busy professional who is looking for an easy, fun, and safe property in a vacation resort community of like-minded lake enthusiasts - schedule a private tour!

First time on the market! This well-maintained home has 3 beds/1.75 baths and sits on a large lot that backs up to trees providing ultra privacy. The huge shop is a hobbyist's dream with multiple rooms/storage that you will never have to leave because it includes an additional shower and toilet! Amazing location - 5 minutes to the border, Birch Bay, and Semiahmoo Resort. Located in the Sunday Harbor community, which offers a boat launch, playground, picnic area, and fire pit on California Creek. A heat pump ensures you stay cool during the hot summer and warm during the cold winter. This is your chance to own a home, shop, and a 10K sq. ft. lot for $375K! Home is being sold by Power of Attorney - buyer to verify all information.

Introducing a meticulously crafted 2024-built residence situated in Whispering Meadows Neighborhood in Nooksack. Discover Modern elegance finishes in a 3-bedroom + office/den w/ 3 full baths. Primary suite upstairs offers a his & her closet, bathroom w/ double vanity, step-in shower. Open kitchen is perfect for culinary enthusiasts, featuring an island, soft close cabinetry w/ large backyard views. The abundance of natural light enhances the space & allows your houseplants to thrive! Office/ den sits next to full bath on main floor. It features a covered front porch & covered deck.Spacious laundry room & ample storage throughout. Home offers the perfect blend of style, comfort, & convenience. Don't miss your chance-schedule your tour today!

Great location on the 7th fairway! This custom-built home in the Stonehaven neighborhood of Semiahmoo is just what you have been waiting for. The great room features an open kitchen, vaulted ceilings, and French doors that open to a raised patio. The main floor includes a primary suite, a private guest suite, and a media room/den. Upstairs, a bright bonus room with a bath serves as additional guest quarters or a home office. The home has been well-maintained, with a new roof in 2023, a stack stone fireplace, & air conditioning. The beautifully landscaped yard completes this wonderful property. Easy access to all resort amenities - golf, pickleball, tennis & health club. Enjoy the best of Semiahmoo living in this lovely, move-in-ready home!

Classic Fairhaven abode on fully master-gardener, landscaped lot. Updated throughout & totally charming! 3 bdrm, 1 full bath, luxury vinyl plank & tile flooring, all appliances stay. Double pane windows, affordable utilities, walking distance to the bay, Marine Park, Ferry Terminal events, train station and all of the Fairhaven shops. Warm, light-filled interior with amazing storage and efficient floor plan. Newer attached 24x16 garage, extra deep, is accessed off the alley w/more off road parking. Fenced back yard is totally private and has a patio for entertaining and a darling, multi-use studio outbuilding surrounded by lush greenery. This property is a charmer for sure, in excellent condition, and in a much sought after location.

Opportunity is Knocking! Great potential for the project minded individual. This two bedroom, two bath home is being sold "As Is", all contents included - A Garage Sale Enthusiasts Paradise. Property has a Water Meter, and the Septic system just passed inspection with flying colours. Walking distance to all amenities: beaches, parks, community centers, post offices, restaurants, library, grocery store, gas stations and even the marina. This won't last long! Check out link to online video tour.

Discover your private sanctuary in Ferndale - a charming 2-bedroom plus HUGE bonus room that could be used as a 3rd room or family room, nestled on almost 10 acres of mainly dry land. Whether you're dreaming of gardens, raising animals, developing or simply enjoying ultimate privacy, this property has it all. With ample space for RV parking or an ADU/shop development and no HOA, the possibilities are endless. Enjoy the fruit trees, nature and detached outbuilding with guests! Your long driveway sets far back from the main road, yielding maximum quiet enjoyment, making this is a rare find. Don't miss out on this unique opportunity in a highly sought out location!

One of the best views on the lake! 60+/- feet of low bank Lake Samish waterfront with a substantial private dock and lake water rights. Value in land, dock & water rights. All of the recreational pursuits await - waterskiing, fishing, kayaking, paddleboarding, swimming. Full view of the lake & foothills beyond. Original cabin with 1939 vintage wood paneling. Post & block foundation on .17 acre. Cabin is 576 SF with 2 BR & 3/4 BA. Come with your plans & ideas for future changes - remodel or new structure! Private well & property is on Lake Samish PUD sewer. This home & property are next to the Calmor Cove Club & you will turn into that property to get to the home. Property & home AS IS, stored items included.

BUYER BONUS AVAILABLE!! Introducing our exquisite 2-story Bluff floorplan featuring 3 beds & 2.75 bathrooms, and 2-car large tandem garage space. Enjoy the spacious deck off the main living area with breathtaking water views over Birch Bay. The primary suite is a true haven, boasting a lavish 5-piece ensuite with free standing tub, custom cabinets, and oversized walk-in closet creating ample space for all your needs. The lower level includes a bonus room for the perfect guest suite or entertainment space. Luxury abounds with ceramic tiles, and high-end appliances in the chef's dream kitchen. Proximity to golf clubs, Semiahmoo, Vancouver BC, and Seattle. Indulge in the epitome of elegance and coastal living. Your perfect oasis awaits.

Charming one-level country-style home boasts 3 bedrooms, 1 bath, and a bonus room on nearly 5 acres of land. The property includes a spacious 30'X50' shop, ideal for various uses. Situated conveniently close to Bellingham and other attractions, this home offers the perfect blend of county living with urban convenience. Inside you will find a large family and dining room area, skylights for natural light, a well appointed kitchen with all new appliances and an island. Step outside to enjoy a peaceful pond and views of Mt. Baker from back deck, which features upgrade trex decking (front and back). Equestrian and other possibilities...Come and see this amazing place.

Fully serviced building lots ideal for your dream or spec home. 3 of 5 lots available. Lots 1, 2 and 4 - these are ready to go with water, sewer, power, gas and cable. Country feel in the city convenient to schools, shopping, city park, restaurants, etc. City of Nooksack cooperative to work with for building permitting. Lot 1 is 10, 704 sq. Ft. Lot 2 is 9610 Sq. Ft. Lot 4 is 9686 sq. ft. Some buffer reduction in place for lot 4. Established residential neighborhood with sidewalks and curbs. Nice affordable option for fully serviced ready to go building lots.

Inspection has been done, most items on report are completed. Located in the popular York neighborhood, this house has 4 bedrooms and a completely new bathroom. New roof, new carpet, new paint throughout home. Keep your dogs safe in the large fully-fenced backyard. 1 car detached garage/shop. Spacious covered front porch for get togethers. Plenty of parking in front of house. This home would make a great starter home or rental. Conveniently located on a quiet street, close to grocery shopping and restaurants.

Discover waterfront luxury in Birch Bay Villages gated paradise. This custom-crafted home blends rich fir & cedar into a contemporary Northwest design. Cherish year-round vistas of Birch Bay, the Strait of Georgia, islands, and Mt. Baker. Spanning 3797 sq. ft. The layout includes main-level living, the Primary bedroom with additional office/bedroom, plus two upper suites, a loft, and a family room with a second kitchen. Radiant floor heating with multiple zones throughout. Air conditioning as well. Chefs kitchen, dining and Great room on the main level. Experience the pinnacle of waterfront living. Birch Bay Village amenities include 24/7 security, golf course, marina, clubhouse, pickleball, tennis, waterfront access, parks & more.

Fully serviced building lots ideal for your dream or spec home. 3 of 5 lots available. Lots 1, 2 and 4 - these are ready to go with water, sewer, power, gas and cable. Country feel in the city convenient to schools, shopping, city park, restaurants, etc. City of Nooksack cooperative to work with for building permitting. Lot 1 is 10, 704 sq. Ft. Lot 2 is 9610 Sq. Ft. Lot 4 is 9686 sq. ft. Some buffer reduction in place for lot 4. Established residential neighborhood with sidewalks and curbs. Nice affordable option for fully serviced ready to go building lots.

Welcome to your beautifully crafted craftsman home complete with tall ceilings, west facing deck with french doors expand the living space to the out doors. The large screen windows throughout the home create a wonderful cross breeze and freshness in the home. Bask in the beautiful views of the South Fork Valley hills on both sides of the house. The house features unique touches such as Mexican sinks and tile. Enjoy a beautiful waterfall view on the Van Zandt dike in the colder winter months. Sunlight streams onto the property a majority of the day. Several mature wild cherry trees and raised garden bed, line the large yard. The perfect space for relaxing or entertaining your guests. Located near Van Zandt park and the South fork river.

Experience the beauty of South Hill in this stunning home with breathtaking views! Inspired by Frank Lloyd Wright, this stylish residence boasts bamboo hardwood floors, two gas fireplaces, stainless steel appliances & honed black quartz waterfall countertops in the kitchen. The abundance of skylights & windows fills the home with natural light. The main level offers everything you need, including a primary suite with a view & private deck access. The lower level provides spacious family room, two bedrooms, full bathroom & separate outdoor entrance. With a private driveway & stairway access from Morey Ave, convenience is key. The low-maintenance yard includes a covered, fenced area under the deck. Move in, relax & savor stunning sunsets!

Step into contemporary luxury with this brand new home nestled in an old growth grove! Boasting an open concept layout, including a chic first-floor mother-in-law suite with private entrance. The suite is complete with a kitchenette, bedroom, and bathroom. The third floor reveals a private primary suite with three closet spaces and bonus room. Enjoy a serene escape on your private 300 sq ft deck surrounded by lush greenery, trail to Beaver Creek and old growth trees. Located in the convenient Gate 13, ten minutes from Bellingham with a flat road and easy winter access. An adventurer's dream, backing onto Stimpson Family Nature Reserve, walking distance to Lookout Mountain, an EV plug in and a 30 second bike ride to access Galbraith trails.

Spread out in this 2516 square foot home, with 1615 square feet on the main living area on the first floor: primary suite, home office, living room, kitchen, dining area, powder room, gas fireplace and utility room. Upstairs has 2 good size bedrooms with a full bath, attic storage and 9 foot ceilings. Living room comes with a gas fireplace, custom shutter blinds and windows for lots of light. Large, sunny backyard is fully fenced. Kitchen and bath countertops are granite. Brand new tile floors in all bathrooms. One side of the double garage accommodates tandem parking or your personal gym. Energy Star refrigerator and dishwasher.

Discover this brand-new home featuring 4 bd, 2 bath, and a bonus room! The well-designed floor plan boasts designer finishes, vaulted ceilings, and a beautiful gas fireplace. The great room, ideal for entertaining, includes a spacious dining area extending from the bright, open kitchen. The kitchen offers ample storage with a walk-in pantry, quartz countertops, a tiled backsplash, and stainless-steel appliances. The main floor master suite includes a walk-in closet and a luxurious master bathroom with a tiled shower, bathtub and double vanity. The main floor also has two additional bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a laundry room. Enjoy a large covered outdoor living area, perfect for gatherings!

Discover the perfect blend of convenience and comfort in this well-maintained home! Ideally situated within walking distance to Barkley Villages vibrant shops, grocery stores, dining options, Theatre, and super-fun Nature Play Park. Low-maintenance and move-in ready all on one level. Floor plan offers BOTH living AND family rooms, 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and an attached 2-car garage. Enjoy the sunny, fully fenced backyard featuring a covered patio for year-round outdoor enjoyment. Freshly painted inside and out with brand new carpet and flooring throughout. New hot water heater in 2024. Trailheads to the Interurban Trail System are a block away. Prime location to all that makes Bellingham great! A delightful place to call Home !

Absolutely irreplaceable building lot bordering national forest service land in the very popular Snowline gated community. This lot has been carved into the hillside making a beautiful flat building site along with all utilities including septic system, water, power etc. Plans and permits are ready to go! This site is so well thought out as to take advantage of the natural beauty of the surrounding temperate forest with towering fir trees, dramatic rock outcroppings, and backing up to forest service land providing an intimate and private setting. Truly a one of a kind whistler-esque setting.

This mid-century home is perched on a hillside behind the Fairhaven Middle School playfields with main floor living and amazing views across Bellingham Bay toward the city with the mountains beyond. The home has a large wraparound deck that leads to the front entry. Once inside, the floor plan is quite open with floor to ceiling windows taking in the views. The lower level has a kitchenette just off the family room with a fireplace and could be a 2 bed/1bath ADU. There is a lovely covered patio area off the kitchen which is great for BBQs and watching the fabulous sunsets! Don't miss the large RV or boat storage shop at the top of the 2nd driveway. Behind the shop there is a grassy area which is ideal for picnics while the sun sets.

Step into this beautifully updated Nooksack gem, built in 2013 and brimming with modern upgrades! Revel in the all-new floors, cabinetry & fresh paint that elevate this homes charm. The great room design features soaring vaulted ceilings & cozy gas fireplace, perfect for gatherings. The lovely kitchen boasts a central island with bar seating, ideal for culinary adventures. Enjoy the privacy of the split bedroom design; the inviting primary suite features a walk in closet & lovely en suite. Ceiling fans in all bedrooms. Separate utility room with sink. Outside, the expansive 10, 890 sq ft lot is fully fenced, featuring a massive 25 x 27 aggregate patio added recently, perfect for outdoor entertaining. This lovely home is a must-see!

Country living just minutes from Barkley Village, schools and Lake Whatcom! This property is a great location for your home construction and private ranch, or farm. This quiet 9+ acre View lot gives you the opportunity for a private retreat just minutes from shopping and work yet in the country. A 4-bedroom septic design is included. The driveway is in, and you have choices where to build, place your shop and or a barn. This property gives you the best of everything. Easy access, quiet location, close to jobs, schools and shopping and Seller is currently working on bringing a District 7 water line to the property. Purchaser is responsible for the hookup. Appointment only access with an agent.

This charming corner top floor unit condo offers an abundance of natural light with it's many windows, complemented by fresh paint and new carpeting throughout. It's immaculate condition, secure parking, and effortless entry make for convenient living. Boasting two bedrooms and 1.75 bathrooms, it also features a clubhouse with a fitness room for recreation. Situated conveniently near I-5 access, restaurants, shopping, and scenic trails and parks, it promises both comfort and convenience for this fortunate occupants. No Rental Cap! (buyer to verify).

Affordable Condo, Amazing Location! Offering one of the most convenient locations in Bellingham, this well-kept condo offers easy walks to grocery stores, restaurants, bars, pools, parks, bus lines, trails and more. 920 Square Feet, 2-Bed, 1.75-bath, with private balcony. This condo is the perfect opportunity to build equity with an affordable home. All the while, paying less in mortgage that you would for most rentals! Extra storage closet outside, appliances included, and your pets welcome on private greens. Dont let this opportunity pass you by.

This solidly constructed building is in a quiet neighborhood of multi-family housing in the City of Ferndale. The location is at the end of a dead-end street. Each of the units has a deep single car garage with storage. Most windows have been upgraded to vinyl in recent years. Each of the units has a patio or deck. The building includes plenty of parking, a great location and with the garages and single level living in each unit they are easy to rent. The units are on annual leases which could be raised closer to the market as they renew. Easy access to shopping, downtown and near the bus route. There is nothing but money to be made with this great investment opportunity!

One of the best locations and values in town! This sunny Alabama Hill home is just steps away from the local trail system leading to Whatcom Falls Park, Lake Whatcom, Galbraith, Barkley and more. First time on the market since construction, this 4 bed / 2 bath home is pre-inspected and ready. Vaulted ceilings, expansive sunny deck off the kitchen, 2 fireplaces, attached garage & a workshop off the garage. The perfect opportunity to bring your vision, customize to your liking and secure a home in a quiet neighborhood close to everything. See this in person before its gone.

Contemporary and eco-friendly, NEW Larrabee Springs Venture Townhomes feature, 8 panel solar system, 2 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, and modern design flooded with natural light. Explore the convenience of sidewalks and sustainable living with solar panels & EV wiring. Elevate the living experience with locally crafted cabinets by the renowned Highcraft Cabinets in Ferndale. Discover the perfect blend of style, functionality, and artisanal quality in these thoughtfully designed townhomes. Reservations Only. Prices subject to change. Showings available between 12pm-3pm, 7 days a week. Larrabee Springs Venture Townhomes

Beautifully Remodeled Ground-Level Corner Unit Near Cordata Park! Step into this move-in-ready condo, freshly remodeled with modern touches throughout. Enjoy brand new laminate flooring that flows seamlessly, and a stunning kitchen upgrade featuring new cabinets, quartz countertops and backsplash. Bathroom remodel includes new flooring, vanities, and a sleek shower insert. The oversized primary bedroom boasts a walk-in closet and an additional sink for added convenience. Second bedroom is generously sized, perfect for use as a guest room &/or home office. With on-site laundry and a private patio overlooking expansive greenery, this unit offers both comfort and tranquility. A perfect place to call home!

Beautiful home, corner lot in desirable Birchwood Neighborhood. 3bed, 2.5bath, large windows provide an abundance of natural light. Walk through your covered porch to open main floor that features hardwood flooring throughout the living room, kitchen, family, laundry & powder room. Kitchen is open to the family/dining, featuring extensive counter space & cabinets with large island. Split stairway to 2nd floor leads to large primary suite w/ walk-in closer and private bath. 2 additional large bedrooms, one w/ walk in closet. A full bath off the hall complete the upstairs. Detached 2 car garage. Large sized yard, mature landscape, fully fenced & garden area. Covered back porch for outdoor cooking. Close to Squalicum Park & Squalicum Beach.

This charming 3-bedroom, 1.75-bathroom home offers serene living in a quiet Lynden location, situated on an expansive 13, 500 square foot, flat lot. The home has been tastefully remodeled and is move-in ready, featuring a gorgeous kitchen with ample cabinet space, a separate dining room perfect for gatherings, and a cozy, clean interior. The primary bedroom is conveniently located on the main floor, while two additional bedrooms are upstairs, along with a 3/4 bath. Unfinished 900 sq ft basement too! Outside, you'll find a detached 3-car garage with plenty of RV parking. This home offers peaceful living with ample outdoor space to relax, play, or entertain. Clean and well-maintained, it's a true gem!

Discover this spacious 3-bedroom, 1.75-bathroom double-wide home, offering 1, 056 sq ft of comfortable living space. Nestled in a desirable area, you'll be just minutes away from Bellingham, Lynden, and Ferndale with easy access to I-5. This charming starter home is a rare find in today's market at an unbeatable price. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity!
